use flake

# Display help on shell entry
cat << 'EOF'

Keyboard Firmware Commands

Build Commands:
  nix build .#totem          - Build Totem firmware (seeeduino_xiao_ble)
  nix build .#eyelash_corne  - Build Eyelash Corne firmware (custom board)
  nix build .#sofle          - Build Sofle firmware (nice_nano_v2)
  nix build .#charybdis      - Build Charybdis firmware (nice_nano_v2)

Flash Commands:
  nix run .#flash-totem         - Flash Totem firmware
  nix run .#flash-eyelash_corne - Flash Eyelash Corne firmware  
  nix run .#flash-sofle         - Flash Sofle firmware
  nix run .#flash-charybdis     - Flash Charybdis firmware

Utility Commands:
  nix run .#update           - Update ZMK dependencies
  nix develop               - Enter development shell

Output: Built firmware appears in ./result/ directory
Manual flash: Copy .uf2 files to bootloader drive when in bootloader mode

EOF
